name: To Bus Terminal
longdescription: Visit the Santa Rosa Complex Balibago, the busiest place in the city. Many establishments can be found here, from a bakery, hardware, electronics, tiange, and food stall.

to.name: Balibago Bus Termininal
to.commute: Ride a jeep with a sign "Complex". The common fare rate is P10

pointOfInterests.name: TNVS Group
pointOfInterests.description: TNVS Group Jeepney and UV Express terminal

pointOfInterests.name: Target Mall
pointOfInterests.description: Take a visit to the most known mall in Santa Rosa. Although it is small, it becomes popular because it was close to bus terminals.
